Date Posted: 2014/05/03 04:32:23Ref. JB1001843313
Business Consultant - SalesBin Murshed Holding
A business consultant is required who have experience in sales
The Job Description:
•	Responsible in generating new business leads by telephone marketing,
bulk emailing,
customer referrals and other marketing tools to promote the company services.
•	Conducts and participate in business center events,
embassy meetings,
business group meetings
•	Consistently achieves the company sales target. (monthly,
quarterly,
semi annually & annually)
•	Market and provide new corporate clients according to the monthly target.
•	Ensure to meet all the activity standards for prospecting calls,
appointments,
presentations,
proposals and close deals.
•	Prepares and finalize contract details with the clients:
(1. Regular retainer contract 2. Case to case no obligation annual contract)
•	Maintains contact with all clients to ensure high level of customer satisfaction.
•	Responsible with accountability and follow-up the transaction details with the Accounts Officer.
•	Adheres to all company policies,
procedures and business ethics codes and ensures that they are communicated and implemented within the team.
Skills
Communication skills
Sales & Marketing
Computer knowledge
language (English,
Arabic & Urdu)
